=Draft a professional email reply to the following PE deal marketing email. The reply should thank them, express interest in learning more about the opportunity, and request the NDA (Non-Disclosure Agreement) so we can review the deal materials.

Mention the specific deal or fund name from the email. Keep it concise and professional. Output ONLY the email body text - no subject line, no greeting header, no signature block.

Original email:
From: {{ $('Fetch Full Email').item.json.from }}
Subject: {{ $('Fetch Full Email').item.json.subject }}

{{ $('Fetch Full Email').item.json.textPlain }}

{{ $('Fetch Full Email').item.json.textHtml }}

=Draft a brief, polite email declining this private equity deal opportunity. Thank them for thinking of us, but indicate we'll pass on this particular opportunity. Keep it professional and leave the door open for future deals.

Original email:
From: {{ $('Fetch Full Email').item.json.from }}
Subject: {{ $('Fetch Full Email').item.json.subject }}

{{ $('Fetch Full Email').item.json.textPlain }}

{{ $('Fetch Full Email').item.json.textHtml }}
